Is the book of Daniel relevant to us today? Discover different prophecy perspectives on this fascinating topic with Truth Matters! This clip explores Catholic, Evangelical, Jewish, and SDA views on the 70-week prophecy, revealing truth amid interpretations. Is there a barrier between God and humanity if they do not fully understand Hebrew? Dive into insights on the Rabbinic curse linked to Daniel 8 and 9.
